OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with plenty of sunshine for
OL,6,Fmuch England and Wales. Cloudier
OL,7,Facross parts of Northern Ireland and
OL,8,FScotland with patchy rain, although
OL,9,Fsome brighter spells developing at
OL,10,Ftimes. Feeling warm for many and hot
OL,11,Ftowards the southeast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA weakening band of cloud and
OL,14,Frain moving across Scotland and
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland this evening, with
OL,16,Ffurther rain arriving into Scotland
OL,17,Fovernight. Remaining dry with clear
OL,18,Fspells elsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
