OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FBand of rain across Scotland
OL,6,Fmoving southeastwards and turning
OL,7,Fincreasingly showery. Remaining dry,
OL,8,Fsunny and very warm across southern
OL,9,Fareas, with brighter and fresher
OL,10,Fconditions following across Scotland.
